title: Tech answers back, tops MSU 7-2 in game two - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Tech answers back, tops MSU 7-2 in game two - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: BILOXI, Miss. – The No. 17 Texas Tech baseball team bounced back Wednesday, defeating No. 23 Mississippi State 7-2 to split the midweek showdown at MGM Park. The Red Raiders improve to 11-3 and have won 10 of their last 11 games.
